title: 10 year thing
body: I got my riot kayle but I didn't get my icon :/

replies.body: There are a ton of eligible accounts, so it's going to take some time before every account receives their gifts.  We'll be keeping updates on the [support ticker.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-)  Hang tight until everything is finished rolling out!
The gifts are not done being distributed. The 23rd is the final day, so if you don't have it by then, you can submit a support ticket.
